      <p><br/>
Suppose you are on a cart initially at rest that rides on a frictionless track. If you throw a ball off the cart towards the  left, will the cart be put into motion?
</p>
    
    <br/>
    <multiplechoiceresponse max="10" direction="vertical" randomize="no" loncapaid="11" type="MultipleChoice">
      <choicegroup type="MultipleChoice">
        <choice location="random" name="foil1" correct="true">

              Yes, and it will move to the right.          
        </choice>
        <choice location="random" name="foil2" correct="false">

              Yes, and it will move to the left.          
        </choice>
        <choice location="random" name="foil3" correct="false">

              No, it will remain in place.          
        </choice>
      </choicegroup>
    </multiplechoiceresponse>
